nodes.text: Denna was a Human male student at the University of Agamar.
In 25 ABY, he was one of the members of Dr. Anki Pace's team to journey to Bimmiel in search of Jedi archives.
He and Vil were captured by the Yuuzhan Vong and placed in the Embrace of Pain. Fortunately, both he and Vil were rescued by Corran Horn and Ganner Rhysode shortly thereafter.
